{"tid":420681,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺，貪錢既人，其實好可悲","createTime":"2017-10-01T15:19:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T06:35:55.000Z","uid":123335,"like":41,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"a5484b272018ce7307e9e7eeb8a25d7a9a59cbdd","tid":420681,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:19:39.000Z","msg":"過份將人生個焦點放係錢銀上面 <br />\n<br />\n人生會miss 左好多野 , e.g. pure love , pure friendship , 有個idea 想做就做既passion ...etc <br />\n<br />\n但出生係香港真係冇計<br />\n命中注定大家都係咁可悲 <br />\n一生為錢奔波勞碌 <br />\n一生被錢牽著鼻子走"},{"pid":"65fce5d4f1847ec32a8d7d78f2bbd7581ec96f15","tid":420681,"uid":134462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:21:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1b4872baf09789bb1496b5cc23ec959be3e70be","tid":420681,"uid":35870,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:22:24.000Z","msg":"有錢唔係萬能，但無錢就萬萬不能"},{"pid":"1b33a6c51bf2d696bc3e9c42313ce818e458fb61","tid":420681,"uid":55445,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:24:04.000Z","msg":"無安全感先貪錢姐<br />\n如果有一世正常駛都駛唔晒既錢我都唔會貪"},{"pid":"824e576ab33a97bd1e31e22021d2c88cd2f9c843","tid":420681,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:25:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有錢唔係萬能，但無錢就萬萬不能</blockquote><br />\n係呀  係香港冇錢點過日子？<br />\n食物質素，住屋環境<br />\n冇錢真係食埋d 垃圾低質野 , 食得多真係生cancer <br />\n冇錢住得差，真係命都短幾年"},{"pid":"35ef05725c1541ad1d1bf0416d36ce5da073eafb","tid":420681,"uid":123335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:29:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無安全感先貪錢姐<br />\n如果有一世正常駛都駛唔晒既錢我都唔會貪</blockquote><br />\n香港唔似歐洲既福利國家咁<br />\n窮人都有得住house 養狗  有花園  有車 有車位 <br />\n醫療資源又好好多 <br />\n真係俾足安全感你去尋找你既自我，尋找屬於你既人生意義，發展夢想"},{"pid":"8eb001d08b863541554d93bb0ccb9869c37692ce","tid":420681,"uid":124899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:37:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有錢唔係萬能，但無錢就萬萬不能</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無限貪既藉口黎啫，你要先定義基本生活需要線，如，三萬蚊<br />\n過左依個數你果句就只係貪婪既藉口黎"},{"pid":"878d11692aa4884d3020e611bb3b2e4cf283a3c2","tid":420681,"uid":72484,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:37:39.000Z","msg":"內文同貪錢有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係香港地逼於無奈要係咁搵錢，先可以有等同外國基本既生活，無錢就連狗都不如，訓街訓公園wfc"},{"pid":"5698f52d2e6c506f070d09a011b030c908cea26c","tid":420681,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:39:15.000Z","msg":"貪撚到咩"},{"pid":"aac2681e7dd46e22f2d3e883bb5410a2c90a6e29","tid":420681,"uid":76105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:40:45.000Z","msg":"你無錢仲可悲"},{"pid":"41dae79fd881c782965291654a016f99bcd4744f","tid":420681,"uid":124899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:40:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>貪撚到咩</blockquote><br />\n差唔多每個人都賭股其實已經係病<br />\n重要用投資去美化"},{"pid":"4b4bd6980cb95b8fef921a131e3681866444bb63","tid":420681,"uid":124899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:41:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你無錢仲可悲</blockquote><br />\n咪就係因為有貪錢既人"},{"pid":"8546def9f8db67dc87899c475c3e85c7de3ccc8a","tid":420681,"uid":124899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:43:24.000Z","msg":"資本家要所有人都卷入佢依個金錢遊戲"},{"pid":"0872b016ab2eda3e20e978872e47db5cf3ec9683","tid":420681,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T02:24:33.000Z","msg":"香港地有錢真係算幾好住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買乜食乜都好快做到<br />\n<br />\n不過見到身邊d朋友<br />\n諗到佢成世將會係咁上下生活 都幾頹下<br />\n除非有橫財"},{"pid":"a090cf43560f15287ba412536017892eb1e66a3f","tid":420681,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T02:27:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港地有錢真係算幾好住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買乜食乜都好快做到<br />\n<br />\n不過見到身邊d朋友<br />\n諗到佢成世將會係咁上下生活 都幾頹下<br />\n除非有橫財</blockquote><br />\n香港冇錢既生活真係食屎咁<br />\n有錢就快活過神仙"},{"pid":"5354946ce29cc9cbeab475df7285687b44c00156","tid":420681,"uid":100716,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T02:31:28.000Z","msg":"返第一份工比貪錢老細呃左我錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  見佢枱頭手機完全無同人的合照 覺得佢個人好無情 為左錢對人好賤"},{"pid":"7f42106076d4e3ce46a090c54ee951b69ed7b1a1","tid":420681,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T02:34:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返第一份工比貪錢老細呃左我錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  見佢枱頭手機完全無同人的合照 覺得佢個人好無情 為左錢對人好賤</blockquote><br />\n通常夠賤果d 幾搵到錢<br />\n因為做決定時唔洗點理會感情因素，淨係會睇錢份上"},{"pid":"addf5c7833820abc953e4ca2c43d84f6a52e63be","tid":420681,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T02:35:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港地有錢真係算幾好住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買乜食乜都好快做到<br />\n<br />\n不過見到身邊d朋友<br />\n諗到佢成世將會係咁上下生活 都幾頹下<br />\n除非有橫財</blockquote><br />\n香港冇錢既生活真係食屎咁<br />\n有錢就快活過神仙</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都窮過 明白個種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係用痛苦形容 係諗一諗個荷包 所有念頭就收左皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家都算環境唔錯 感恩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a910dc997db1fc81a5c129c911931bfb6f1632e5","tid":420681,"uid":17116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T02:38:20.000Z","msg":"唔貪錢好多人已經咬梗老綜喇"},{"pid":"5471dcc20d60e76670652fb97f80d1a4a569e92b","tid":420681,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T02:41:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔貪錢好多人已經咬梗老綜喇</blockquote><br />\n咬老再秘撈既人最撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"889f947d0f9b01d99f5f5d69cf7ba4106961d6b0","tid":420681,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T02:43:55.000Z","msg":"滿足基本所需，再拼盡力氣搵錢勉強可以叫貪，如果衣食住行係基本所需，係香港應該好少人叫貪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n同埋有人天生個夢想就係做成功既businessman, 佢地追尋自己夢想有咩唔啱？"},{"pid":"2c70a39bf3a431887782396af26f7e559cdea64e","tid":420681,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T02:46:49.000Z","msg":"人地要pure money唔得？<br />\n要錢唔等於無其他野"},{"pid":"72b57f79499b687c0a0531c768cbb9725ff21fe6","tid":420681,"uid":61510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T03:49:21.000Z","msg":"貪錢好過貪權"},{"pid":"83d378ef6ae6b482fdaf752b4c8acfb59a98f13a","tid":420681,"uid":23385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T03:58:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>貪錢好過貪權</blockquote><br />\nwhy not both<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9d4d60addf4e029c4c4f72db197adfdd9b22c9a","tid":420681,"uid":128953,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:51:38.000Z","msg":"貪錢？其實係想要更多既自由。錢限制左我地好多好多既想法，行動。<br />\n係呢個社會，冇錢想做乜都有限制，想食個飯都要三思，冇錢連衣食住行都受錢限制既時候，何來自由。<br />\n有錢可以解決最基本既衣食住行問題，更有多餘時，可以好多自己想做既事，可以去遠D，唔洗諗機票幾錢。<br />\n另外，有錢食乜女都得，冇錢連臭雞都睇你唔起。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以，比心機搵錢，搵多D錢，咁先有錢食多D女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}